data.description: Welcome to your new home! This charming four-bedroom, two-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience, boasting a generous 1649 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space.    As you step through the front door, you're greeted by a welcoming entryway that seamlessly flows into the spacious living room-an ideal space for relaxation and entertainment. The heart of the home lies in the well-appointed kitchen, complete with a dining area and a convenient island, perfect for casual meals or culinary creations.  The owner's suite is a retreat within itself, featuring ample space, and a luxurious ensuite bathroom that includes a separate shower and tub. The sizable closet provides an abundance of storage, ensuring that you have room for all your wardrobe essentials.  This home offers versatility with two additional bedrooms, each providing comfort and style. The third bedroom can easily be transformed into a home office, catering to the modern lifestyle's demand for flexible living spaces.    Step outside into the expansive backyard, where a large, lush lawn awaits. The presence of a mature tree adds both character and shade, creating an inviting outdoor space for gatherings or personal relaxation.    Conveniently situated near restaurants and grocery stores, this home combines the tranquility of a residential neighborhood with the ease of access to amenities. Whether you're enjoying the comfort of your well-designed interior or exploring the nearby local attractions, this home is a perfect blend of style, functionality, and location. Your dream lifestyle begins here-schedule a showing today!
